    <text><![CDATA[<p><strong>Hint 2 (Formulas):</strong> Capacitor = open circuit at DC (blocks DC current). Inductor = short circuit at DC (zero voltage drop). For a series RLC circuit: \(\alpha = \frac{R}{2L}\), \(\omega_0 = \frac{1}{\sqrt{LC}}\).</p>]]></text>
